#. <section class="sutta" id="sn3.20"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn3.20:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 3"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 3"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn3.20:0.2"
msgid "2. Dutiyavagga"
msgstr "2. Childless"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn3.20:0.3"
msgid "20. Dutiyaaputtakasutta"
msgstr "20. Childless (2nd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.206"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn3.20:1.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho rājā pasenadi kosalo divā divassa yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; "
"upasaṅkamitvā ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho rājānaṃ pasenadiṃ kosalaṃ bhagavā "
"etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then King Pasenadi of Kosala went up to the Buddha in the middle of the day …"
" The Buddha said to him:"

msgctxt "sn3.20:1.2"
msgid "“handa kuto nu tvaṃ, mahārāja, āgacchasi divā divassā”ti?"
msgstr "“So, great king, where are you coming from in the middle of the day?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts1ed" id="pts1ed1.92"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn3.20:2.1"
msgid "“Idha, bhante, sāvatthiyaṃ seṭṭhi gahapati kālaṅkato."
msgstr "“Sir, here in Sāvatthī a financier householder has passed away."

msgctxt "sn3.20:2.2"
msgid "Tamahaṃ aputtakaṃ sāpateyyaṃ rājantepuraṃ atiharitvā āgacchāmi."
msgstr ""
"Since he died childless, I have come after transferring his fortune to the "
"royal compound."

msgctxt "sn3.20:2.3"
msgid "Sataṃ, bhante, satasahassāni hiraññasseva, ko pana vādo rūpiyassa."
msgstr "There was ten million in gold, not to speak of the silver."

msgctxt "sn3.20:2.4"
msgid ""
"Tassa kho pana, bhante, seṭṭhissa gahapatissa evarūpo bhattabhogo ahosi—"
msgstr "And yet that financier ate meals of"

msgctxt "sn3.20:2.5"
msgid "kaṇājakaṃ bhuñjati bilaṅgadutiyaṃ."
msgstr "rough gruel with pickles."

msgctxt "sn3.20:2.6"
msgid "Evarūpo vatthabhogo ahosi—"
msgstr "He wore clothes consisting of"

msgctxt "sn3.20:2.7"
msgid "sāṇaṃ dhāreti tipakkhavasanaṃ."
msgstr "three pieces of sunn hemp."

msgctxt "sn3.20:2.8"
msgid "Evarūpo yānabhogo ahosi—"
msgstr "He traveled around in a vehicle that was"

msgctxt "sn3.20:2.9"
msgid "jajjararathakena yāti paṇṇachattakena dhāriyamānenā”ti."
msgstr "a dilapidated little cart, holding a leaf as sunshade.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn3.20:3.1"
msgid "“Evametaṃ, mahārāja, evametaṃ, mahārāja."
msgstr "“That’s so true, great king! That’s so true!"

msgctxt "sn3.20:3.2"
msgid ""
"Bhūtapubbaṃ so, mahārāja, seṭṭhi gahapati taggarasikhiṃ nāma "
"paccekasambuddhaṃ piṇḍapātena paṭipādesi."
msgstr ""
"Once upon a time, great king, that financier householder provided alms-food "
"on behalf of a Buddha awakened for himself named Tagarasikhī."

msgctxt "sn3.20:3.3"
msgid "‘Detha samaṇassa piṇḍan’ti vatvā uṭṭhāyāsanā pakkāmi."
msgstr ""
"He instructed: ‘Give alms to that ascetic,’ before getting up from his seat "
"and leaving."

msgctxt "sn3.20:3.4"
msgid "Datvā ca pana pacchā vippaṭisārī ahosi:"
msgstr "But after giving he regretted it:"

msgctxt "sn3.20:3.5"
msgid "‘varametaṃ piṇḍapātaṃ dāsā vā kammakarā vā bhuñjeyyun’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘It would have been better to feed the bondservants or workers with that "
"alms-food.’"

msgctxt "sn3.20:3.6"
msgid "Bhātu ca pana ekaputtakaṃ sāpateyyassa kāraṇā jīvitā voropesi."
msgstr ""
"What’s more, he murdered his brother’s only child for the sake of his "
"fortune."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts1ed" id="pts1ed1.93"></a>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.207"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn3.20:4.1"
msgid ""
"Yaṃ kho so, mahārāja, seṭṭhi gahapati taggarasikhiṃ paccekasambuddhaṃ "
"piṇḍapātena paṭipādesi, tassa kammassa vipākena sattakkhattuṃ sugatiṃ saggaṃ "
"lokaṃ upapajji."
msgstr ""
"Because that financier provided Tagarasikhī with alms-food, as a result of "
"that deed he was reborn seven times in a good place, a heavenly realm."

msgctxt "sn3.20:4.2"
msgid ""
"Tasseva kammassa vipākāvasesena imissāyeva sāvatthiyā sattakkhattuṃ "
"seṭṭhittaṃ kāresi."
msgstr ""
"And as a residual result of that same deed he held the position of financier "
"seven times right here in Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn3.20:4.3"
msgid "Yaṃ kho so, mahārāja, seṭṭhi gahapati datvā pacchā vippaṭisārī ahosi:"
msgstr "But because that financier regretted giving alms,"

msgctxt "sn3.20:4.4"
msgid ""
"‘varametaṃ piṇḍapātaṃ dāsā vā kammakarā vā bhuñjeyyun’ti, tassa kammassa "
"vipākena nāssuḷārāya bhattabhogāya cittaṃ namati, nāssuḷārāya vatthabhogāya "
"cittaṃ namati, nāssuḷārāya yānabhogāya cittaṃ namati, nāssuḷārānaṃ pañcannaṃ "
"kāmaguṇānaṃ bhogāya cittaṃ namati."
msgstr ""
"as a result of that deed his mind didn’t tend to enjoy nice food, clothes, "
"vehicles, or the five refined kinds of sensual stimulation."

msgctxt "sn3.20:4.5"
msgid ""
"Yaṃ kho so, mahārāja, seṭṭhi gahapati bhātu ca pana ekaputtakaṃ sāpateyyassa "
"kāraṇā jīvitā voropesi, tassa kammassa vipākena bahūni vassāni bahūni "
"vassasatāni bahūni vassasahassāni bahūni vassasatasahassāni niraye paccittha."
msgstr ""
"And because that financier murdered his brother’s only child for the sake of "
"his fortune, as a result of that deed he burned in hell for many years, for "
"many hundreds, many thousands, many hundreds of thousands of years."

msgctxt "sn3.20:4.6"
msgid ""
"Tasseva kammassa vipākāvasesena idaṃ sattamaṃ aputtakaṃ sāpateyyaṃ rājakosaṃ "
"paveseti."
msgstr ""
"And as a residual result of that same deed for the seventh time, since he is "
"childless, his fortune ends up in the royal treasury."

msgctxt "sn3.20:4.7"
msgid ""
"Tassa kho, mahārāja, seṭṭhissa gahapatissa purāṇañca puññaṃ parikkhīṇaṃ, "
"navañca puññaṃ anupacitaṃ."
msgstr ""
"Now the old merit of that financier has been used up, and he hasn’t "
"accumulated new merit."

msgctxt "sn3.20:4.8"
msgid "Ajja pana, mahārāja, seṭṭhi gahapati mahāroruve niraye paccatī”ti."
msgstr "Today, great king, that financier burns in the Great Hell of Screams.”"

msgctxt "sn3.20:4.9"
msgid "“Evaṃ, bhante, seṭṭhi gahapati mahāroruvaṃ nirayaṃ upapanno”ti."
msgstr "“So, sir, that financier has been reborn in the Great Hell of Screams?”"

msgctxt "sn3.20:4.10"
msgid "“Evaṃ, mahārāja, seṭṭhi gahapati mahāroruvaṃ nirayaṃ upapanno”ti."
msgstr "“Yes he has, great king.”"

msgctxt "sn3.20:4.11"
msgid "Idamavoca … pe …."
msgstr "That is what the Buddha said. …"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn3.20:5.1"
msgid "“Dhaññaṃ dhanaṃ rajataṃ jātarūpaṃ,"
msgstr "“Grain, wealth, silver, and gold,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn3.20:5.2"
msgid "Pariggahaṃ vāpi yadatthi kiñci;"
msgstr "or whatever other possessions there are;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn3.20:5.3"
msgid "Dāsā kammakarā pessā,"
msgstr "bondservants, workers, employees,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn3.20:5.4"
msgid "Ye cassa anujīvino."
msgstr "and those dependent for their livelihood:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
#. VAR: Sabbaṃ nādāya → sabbannādāya (s1-3)
msgctxt "sn3.20:6.1"
msgid "Sabbaṃ nādāya gantabbaṃ,"
msgstr "you must go on without taking these;"

#. <br>
#. VAR: nikkhippagāminaṃ → nikkhīpagāminaṃ (s1-3, km, mr)
msgctxt "sn3.20:6.2"
msgid "sabbaṃ nikkhippagāminaṃ;"
msgstr "all of them are left behind."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn3.20:6.3"
msgid "Yañca karoti kāyena,"
msgstr "But the deeds you do"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn3.20:6.4"
msgid "vācāya uda cetasā."
msgstr "by body, speech, and mind—"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "sn3.20:7.1"
msgid "Tañhi tassa sakaṃ hoti,"
msgstr "that’s what you can call your own."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn3.20:7.2"
msgid "taṃva ādāya gacchati;"
msgstr "That’s what you take when you go."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn3.20:7.3"
msgid "Taṃvassa anugaṃ hoti,"
msgstr "That’s what goes with you,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn3.20:7.4"
msgid "chāyāva anapāyinī."
msgstr "like a shadow that never leaves."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.209"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "sn3.20:8.1"
msgid "Tasmā kareyya kalyāṇaṃ,"
msgstr "That’s why you should do good,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn3.20:8.2"
msgid "nicayaṃ samparāyikaṃ;"
msgstr "investing in the future life."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn3.20:8.3"
msgid "Puññāni paralokasmiṃ,"
msgstr "The good deeds of sentient beings"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn3.20:8.4"
msgid "patiṭṭhā honti pāṇinan”ti."
msgstr "support them in the next world.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn3.20:8.5"
msgid "Dutiyo vaggo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "sn3.20:9.1"
msgid "Jaṭilā pañca rājāno,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn3.20:9.2"
msgid "Doṇapākakurena ca;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn3.20:9.3"
msgid "Saṅgāmena dve vuttāni,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
#. VAR: Mallikā → dhītarā (bj, s1-3, km) | dhitarā (pts1)
msgctxt "sn3.20:9.4"
msgid "Mallikā dve appamādena ca;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn3.20:9.5"
msgid "Aputtakena dve vuttā,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn3.20:9.6"
msgid "Vaggo tena pavuccatīti."
msgstr ""
